textfsm_template:
Value NAME_SERVER (\S+)
Value HOST (\S+)
Value IPV4 (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value IPV6 ([0-9a-f:]+)

Start
  ^Name-server:\s+${NAME_SERVER}\s*$$ -> Next.Record
  ^Host\s+Address\(es\)\s*$$
  ^\s*${HOST}\s+${IPV4}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*${HOST}\s+${IPV4}\s+${IPV6}\s*$$ -> Record
